	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Hodie expectamus legatos nostros missos ad regem Gallię; scripserunt autem in hęc verba:</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="de" type="manual">Nachdem als sy verhört sindt von k[öniglicher] m[ajestat], ist ein antwort gefallen: 1. So das regiment zuͦ <placeName type="auto_name">Ensesheim</placeName> alle gefangenen ußlast one alle entgeltnuß, ouch, so eim etwas were genomen, das im restituieren on allen synen kosten, 2° Das sy niemants furterhin verhinderen wellen, die zuͦr kron von Franckreich welle ziehen, ein freye baß geben für und für, 3° Das sy wellent annemen, das uff dem nehsten reichstag werde gehandlet, 4° Das sy willig wellen syn, so er ein schatzung wurde uff sy legen, ouch im probant zuͦ schicken nach syner notturfft: <foreign xml:lang="la">si hos articulos iuraverint se servaturos, regem ab omni persecutione et incursione velle hanc regionem servare.</foreign></s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid hoc est?</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rex <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinandus</persName> id non faciet, aut si promiserit nunc temporis, non servaturus est.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vestri legati apud nos sunt, expectant nostros, qui hodie venient a rege splendide excepti et honorifice dimissi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsit etiam d. <persName type="auto_name">Schertlinus</persName> (cui hodie misi libellum tuum per certum nuncium in castra) non omnibus esse credendum, qui varia spargant de isto bello ac de <persName ref="p18250" cert="high">Mauricio</persName> duce.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salvas esse res bellicas.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentina</placeName> adhuc se non dedit, misit tertiam legationem ad regem, et scribit <persName ref="p8374" cert="high">Hedio</persName> legatos istos, qui 7. maii missi sunt ad regem, aut pacem aut bellum allaturos.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Comitia habentur <placeName ref="l569" cert="high">Wormatiae</placeName> ab episcopis, Trevirensi, <placeName ref="l267" cert="high">Coloniensi</placeName>, Moguntino, Wormaciensi et Spirensi; etiam <persName type="auto_name">Palatinus</persName> cum baronibus et nobilibus praesentes sunt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quidnam <persName type="auto_name">Gallo</persName> respondendum sit, consultabunt.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Varii praeterea rumores sparguntur, de quibus scripsi per <persName ref="p5189" cert="high">Heldium</persName>, <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augustanum</placeName> concionatorem.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nos nihil omnino de <persName type="auto_name">Mauriciano</persName> exercitu audimus.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nobilitas tota territa est tam in <placeName type="auto_name">Sungavia</placeName> quam in <placeName type="auto_name">Brisagoia</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miles sine duce haeret nescio in quo loco; ad nos confluxerunt ingens nobilium multitudo cum uxoribus et liberis.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileę</placeName> 10. maii 1552.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Gastius</persName> ex animo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l1122" cert="high">Parma</placeName> liberata est ab obsidione.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid si <persName ref="p18538" cert="high">Cęsar</persName> hunc exercitum sibi adiungeret?</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Brevi ad vos veniet filius <persName ref="p4744" cert="high">Pauli Fagii</persName> demortui, a quo quę in Anglia agantur, fuse audietis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominis piissimis et doctissimis <persName ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodoro Bibliandro</persName> et m. Henrycho Bullingero, suis in domino observandissimis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zurich.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
